                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> As he was going to the Computer, a young lad said to him, "Dick, never mind, it will only be for a night"—I did not appear before the Alderman the morning, but he sent for me.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner put in a written Defence that on the night in question he was passing along, and saw a mob gathered together that he went to see what was the matter, when he was charged with stealing the handkerchief.)</p>
